@@TJvApplication.Hint
Description:
This is the Application hint

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.HintColor
Description:
This is the color of the hints (the background)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.HintHidePause
Description:
This is the time to let the hint visible

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.HintPause
Description:
This is the time to wait before to show the hint

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.HintShortcuts
Description:
Specifies whether the Application’s pop-up hints include shortcut information.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.HintShortPause
Description:
Specifies the pause to wait before bringing up a hint if a hint has already been shown

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnActionExecute
Description:
This event is called when an action is executed

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnActionUpdate
Description:
This event is called when an action’s Update method is called and its action list has not already handled it.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnActivate
Description:
This event is called when the Application is activated

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnDeactivate
Description:
This event is called when the Application is deactivated

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnException
Description:
This event is called when an Exception is raised

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnHelp
Description:
This event is called when the help is requested by the user

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnHint
Description:
This event is called when a hint is showed

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnIdle
Description:
This event is called when the Application is IDLE

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnMessage
Description:
This event is called when the Application receive a message

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnMinimize
Description:
This event is called when the Application is minimized

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnRestore
Description:
This event is called when the Application is restored

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnShortcut
Description:
This event is called when the user push a key

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.OnShowHint
Description:
This event is called when a hint is about to be showed

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvApplication.ShowHints
Description:
Determines whether Help Hints are enabled or disabled for the entire Application

